high_descs: Walk to the rag on the left side of the tub.
Pick up the leftmost rag in the tub.
Turn around and walk to the sink on the left.
Rinse the rag in the sink on the left and then pick up the rag from the sink.
Turn right and walk to the tub.
Place the rag in the middle of the tub.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean rag in the middle of the tub.

high_descs: Pick up the dirty cloth on the left side of the tub
Turn to your left and head to the sink
Rinse the cloth on the sink with water
Turn right and head to the tub
Put the clean cloth on the left side of the tub
anns.task_desc: Clean the dirty cloth put back on the tub

high_descs: Go straight ahead to the bath tub.
Pick up the washcloth on the left side of inside the tub.
Take the washcloth and turn around. Find the sink on the right side.
Place the washcloth in the sink, on the left side and turn the water on. Turn the water off and pick up the washcloth.
Turn to the right and go back to the bath tub with the washcloth.
Place the washcloth in the bath tub, around the middle.
anns.task_desc: Rinse a washcloth and take it to the bath tub.
